Devon Odessa https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Devon_Odessa 0 Devon Odessa (born January 18, 1974) is an American actress best known for her role as Sharon Cherski on My So-Called Life. Odessa was born in Parkersburg, West Virginia, and brought up on a farm until moving to New Orleans, Louisiana, and later to Los Angeles, California. She graduated from Notre Dame High School in Sherman Oaks in 1992. Devon_Odessa ( born January_18_,_1974 ) is an_American_actress best_known for her_role as Sharon_Cherski on My_So-Called_Life .
